@NODE Introduction
@{line}@{jcenter}
@{bg highlight} Introduction @{bg back}@{line}
@{jleft}@{line}

     McAgenda wants to be a simple phonebook. I have written it to get rid of all those big applications which require you to wander through plenty of options just to get a phone number. I'd rather use paper phonebooks for that. :)@{line}

     Or maybe i'd rather have used, because now there is McAgenda!@{line}

     McAgenda needs OS2.0+ and "reqtools.library" (© Nico François & Magnus Holmgren).@{line}

@ENDNODE


